      "comment": "MIDGET EMERALD (3) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Maiden at this track. Can turn form around here. JADE CLOVER (1) flew the lids and led throughout to get off the mark with her maiden win, then finished a 5 length third last start at Capalaba over 366m (20.19). Maiden this journey but has some solid runs behind her. Can measure up this time. AUSTRIAN ROSE (6) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at this track over 300m (17.11). Will give the top chances plenty to think about. VELVET DASH (5) comes into calculations after showing dash and filling a placing most recently.",
